"CC-0075446-CR2-1.pdf>`__, `セキュリティターゲット "
"<https://commoncriteriaportal.org/files/epfiles/NSCIB-"
"CC-0075446_2-STLite.pdf>`__, `Java Card Protection Profile - Open "
